xxl.core.io.propertyList

Class PropertyListPrinter

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.io.propertyList.PropertyListPrinter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JSONPrinter

    public abstract class PropertyListPrinter
extends Object
    This is an abstract base class for printers which converts a PropertyList into a specific output format. The format and handling or discarding of e.g. complex data type assignments depends on the concrete implementation of the printer.

    The given PropertyList is accessible through the protected member mPropertyList. Any subclass has to implement the abstract method print(OutputStream).
    See Also:
    Print the content of PropertyList as JSON file
